<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">伐柯</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contsone8d80dc931b5">
伐柯如何？匪斧不克。取妻如何？匪媒不得。<br />伐柯伐柯，其则不远。我觏之子，笾豆有践。
</div>
</div>
